article.headline: Stony Brook 56, Lehigh 49
article.story: STONY BROOK, N.Y. (AP) -- Mitchell Beauford had 16 points to help rally Stony Brook to a 56-49 win over Lehigh on Saturday. Cori Spencer added 14 points and 10 rebounds for the Seawolves (3-2). Jose Olivero scored 17 of his 23 points in the first half for the Mountain Hawks (3-3), who led 32-30 at the break and shot 55 percent. They went 2-for-32 in the second half. Stony Brook closed the game on a 10-4 run, led by Bobby Santiago's two jumpers.
